##I didn't know you were here

WECHAT denganqing1984

Feature description, here, I will share my writing, reading the book.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
(I)

Go to a chicken farm and buy chickens. Walk with father to the chicken farm ten meters away.
He paused. "Is there a dog over there? "
I looked ahead. "I don't think so. "
He still does not trust: "You go you go, I wait for you here. "
I smiled and said, "are you so afraid of dogs? "
Father said: "Who is afraid? I Walk Tired, waiting for you here. "
After going home, I told my mother about this, my mother said: "He oh, I just married him, go with relatives, there is a small Mutt at the door, only a call, he hid behind me! "

(II)
On another occasion, after a walk to the Levee, I came back to find my father standing by the sign in the distance. I went up to him, and he ignored me. I called him again, but he didn't answer. I tapped him on the shoulder.
He looked back, a look of surprise: "Qing Er, you see me? "
I said, "I saw you from twenty meters away. "
"I was hiding here, " he said, shaking his head
I said, "Dad, I'm not blind. "
He said, "just pretend you didn't see me. "

(III)

Gradually dusk, the sun gradually inclined down.
After a long walk, my father was tired and sat down.
When I asked him what he was thinking, he said, "sometimes it feels good. "
When I asked how it would be good, he smiled again and got up and said, "let's walk again. "

(D)
Down to the front room, the TV was still on, and the father was asleep on the couch, the sun shining down on him. I crept over to look at him, and he might sense that someone was opening their eyes slowly.
I said, "go back to sleep. "
Father said: "really warm, their home do not know why son fell asleep. "
Then I asked him what he was laughing at.
He said, "when I opened my eyes, I didn't know you were here. "

(V)
My father came to my room to inspect the work, put me up, look at my computer: "You didn't write me today? "
I said, "No. "
My father said: "The front and back of the House you write, why don't you write about me? "
I replied, "I just don't write. "
My father sighed: "I really can not afford to read because of poor, if I read a book, write up much better than you... you do not frivolous! "
And then, he walked away with his head held high, not even looking at me.
(VI)
In the morning I put down a pot of noodles and filled a bowl for my father.
Halfway through the meal, I asked, "Is it good? "
Father Leng for a while, only to see his eyes like a mengju hunting rabbit general stampede, after half a minute to sigh said: "delicious... My son Tube do son all delicious... "
I finished a bowl, went to the kitchen counter to see, "there is still pot. "
Immediately came a response, "I do not want! You all shovel! Delicious you eat more! "

(VII)
I Soak my feet with my father. I take pictures.
He said, "there's nothing to shoot here! Just shoot me as I am old. When I was young, you didn't shoot me. "
I said, "I wasn't born when you were young. "
He said: "That is a pity, you ask your mother, I look like a young! "
Mother poked her head out of the kitchen. "Shame on you! "
